                                <p>Manage your vehicles in the <strong>
                                                <font class="text-o-color-1">Fleet</font>
                                        </strong>
                                        app.</p>
                                <p>
                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm"
                                                href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/master/applications/hr/fleet.html">üéì
                                                Fleet</a>
                                        <br>
                                </p>
